></button>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<nav class=\"gcweb-menu\" typeof=\"SiteNavigationElement\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Menu</h2>\n<button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Main </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/travel.html\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports.html\">Canadian passports and other travel documents</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwstitle section\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nGet urgent, express or emergency weekend passport services</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-natural-disaster-en\"></span>\n<!--<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n  <details>\n    <summary><strong>Wildfires in parts of Canada may affect the mail delivery of passports or other travel documents</strong> </summary>\n    <p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/contact-passport-program.html\">Contact us if you need your passport or travel document <strong>urgently</strong></a> and you:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>can’t access your mail,&nbsp;<strong>and</strong></li>\n      <li>asked to have your passport or other travel document delivered to you</li>\n    </ul>\n  </details>\n</div>-->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-post-strike-en\" id=\"long\"></span>\n<!-- <div class=\"ajax\"> <span data-incl-name=\"passport-post-strike-en\" id=\"long\"></span>\n  <div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n    <details>\n  <summary>\n    <h2 class=\"h4\">Passport services are available during the Canada Post labour disruption</h2>\n  </summary>\n  <p>We’re processing passport applications as usual. However, you <strong>may</strong> experience some delays receiving your passport by mail following recent Canada Post labour disruptions.</p>\n  <p><a href=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/canada-post-2025.html\">Learn how we’re delivering passports during the labour disruption</a>.</p>\n</details>\n  </div>\n</div>-->\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n<h2 class=\"h4\">Possible passport delivery delays</h2>\n<p>We’re processing passport applications as usual. However, you <strong>may</strong> experience some delays receiving your passport by mail following recent Canada Post labour disruptions.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>If you need your passport faster, you may be able to get one of these services:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>urgent pick-up (by the end of next business day)</li>\n<li>express pick-up (2 to 9 business days)\n  \t<ul>\n<li><a aria-controls=\"express-differences\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#express-differences\" role=\"button\">Some locations</a> take at least 3 or 4 business days to process express applications.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>emergency weekend or statutory holiday service</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can request these services</p>\n<ul>\n<li>when you apply in person</li>\n<li>after you apply, but you now need your passport sooner</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To get the services, you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>need to <a aria-controls=\"passport\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#passport\" role=\"button\">provide the necessary documents</a></li>\n<li>may have to pay additional fees</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"express-differences\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<p class=\"modal-title\">Some locations take at least 3 or 4 business days to process express applications.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Express service usually means you’ll get your passport in 2 to 9 business days.</p>\n<p>However, the following locations take slightly longer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.servicecanada.gc.ca/tbsc-fsco/sc-dsp.jsp?rc=5987&amp;lang=eng\" rel=\"external\">Kelowna, British Columbia</a>\n<ul>\n<li>4 to 9 business days</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.servicecanada.gc.ca/tbsc-fsco/sc-dsp.jsp?rc=2383&amp;lang=eng\" rel=\"external\">Pointe-Claire, Quebec</a>\n<ul>\n<li>4 to 9 business days</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.servicecanada.gc.ca/tbsc-fsco/sc-dsp.jsp?rc=1959&amp;lang=eng\" rel=\"external\">Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island</a>\n<ul>\n<li>3 to 9 business days</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"passport\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<p class=\"h2 modal-title\">You must provide proof that you  need the passport</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Proof  you need the passport can be</p>\n<ul>\n<li>an airline, bus or train ticket\n        <ul>\n<li>If travelling by car, a written statement explaining why you need to travel</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>a travel itinerary showing proof of payment</li>\n<li>proof of illness or death in the family requiring you to travel</li>\n<li>a written statement from you or a third party explaining why you need the passport\n        <ul>\n<li>For example, for legal, banking or residency requirements</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If we can’t deliver the passport in time to you or your child, we aren’t liable for any losses.</p>\n<p><strong>We recommend that you don’t finalize any travel plans until you get your passport.</strong></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h2>Instructions to get urgent or emergency services</h2>\n<p>Answer the following questions to learn about your next steps.</p>\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld hidden gc-font-2019\" id=\"ff\">\n<form>\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n            \"noForm\" : true,\n            \"renderas\":\"radio\",\n\t\t\t\"gcChckbxrdio\":true,\n            \"base\": { \"live\": true, \"renderas\":\"radio\",\"gcChckbxrdio\":true},\n            \"hideelm\": \".pe, .result1, .result2, .result3, .result4, .result5\",\n            \"unhideelm\": \"#ff\",\n            \"default\": {\n                \"action\" : \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".pe, .result1, .result2, .result3, .result4, .result5\"\n            },\n            \"reset\": {\n                \"action\" : \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".pe, .result1, .result2, .result3, .result4, .result5\"\n            }\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n        }'>\n<p>Where are you right now?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In Canada\n          <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\">\n<p>Have you already applied?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result5\"}'><a href=\"#result5\">Yes</a></li>\n<li>No\n                <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\">\n<p>What do you need?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result1\"}'><a href=\"#result1\">Adult passport renewal</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result2\"}'><a href=\"#result2\">New adult passport</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result3\"}'><a href=\"#result3\">Child passport</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result4\"}'><a href=\"#result4\">Outside Canada</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"result1\">\n<h2 id=\"result1\">I urgently need to renew an adult passport in Canada</h2>\n<p>On the following page, tell us when you need the passport.</p>\n<p>We’ll then explain how to renew your passport urgently, including which locations offer express, urgent or emergency service.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-call-to-action\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/renew-adult-passport/submit-form-fees.html\">How to renew your passport in Canada</a></p>\n<h3>We can’t guarantee that you’ll get your passport on time.</h3>\n<p>For example, you may not get a passport within your timeline if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there are security concerns with your application or</li>\n<li>your application is incomplete</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"result2\">\n<h2 id=\"result2\">I urgently need a new adult passport in Canada</h2>\n<p>On the following page, tell us when you need the passport.</p>\n<p>We’ll then explain how to apply for an adult passport urgently, including which locations offer express, urgent or emergency service.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-call-to-action\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/new-adult-passport/submit-form-fees.html\">How to apply for an adult passport in Canada</a></p>\n<h3>We can’t guarantee that you’ll get your passport on time.</h3>\n<p>For example, you may not get a passport within your timeline if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there are security concerns with your application or</li>\n<li>your application is incomplete</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"result3\">\n<h2 id=\"result3\">I urgently need a child passport in Canada</h2>\n<p>On the following page, tell us when you need the passport. </p>\n<p>We’ll then explain how to apply for a child passport urgently, including which locations offer express, urgent or emergency service.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-call-to-action\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/child-passport.html#instructions\">How to apply for a child passport in Canada</a></p>\n<h3>We can’t guarantee that you’ll get your passport on time.</h3>\n<p>For example, you may not get a passport within your timeline if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there are security concerns with your application or</li>\n<li>your application is incomplete</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"result4\">\n<h2 id=\"result4\">I’m outside Canada and need a passport urgently</h2>\n<p>Contact the nearest Government of Canada office abroad. They’ll decide if you qualify for urgent services.</p>\n<div class=\"well well-sm\">\n<p>If you need urgent help while abroad, <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/emergency-assistance\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">request emergency assistance<span class=\"wb-inv\"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span>.</p>\n</div>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-call-to-action\" href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\">Find the closest Government of Canada office</a></p>\n<h3>We can’t guarantee that you’ll get your passport on time.</h3>\n<p>For example, you may not get a passport within your timeline if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there are security concerns with your application or</li>\n<li>your application is incomplete</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"result5\">\n<h2 id=\"result5\">Contact us for help</h2>\n<p>If you already applied for a passport and now need it within the next 9 business days or less, call us.</p>\n<p>We’ll help you find a way to get your passport urgently. Extra fees may apply.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-call-to-action\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/contact-passport-program.html\">Call us</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-09-09\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Canadian passports and other travel documents</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre.html\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/contact-passport-program.html\">Contact us</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gc-main-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Government of Canada</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/contact.html\">All contacts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/dept.html\">Departments and agencies<